data.name: Yellowstone Beer Fest
data.description:
The Yellowstone Beer Fest is a regional beer fest held in Cody, Wyoming with five hours of fun, unlimited sampling, food vendors, and live music. Offering local and regional award winning craft beers from Cody, Wyoming, Colorado, Montana, Oregon, Washington, California, Alaska, Utah, Illinois, and Hawaii. There will be some limited release and unique beer available. Featuring around 80+ different beers in all!
Yellowstone Beer Fest is a recently established Non-Profit Organization with proceeds donated to local charities. Must be 21 years old.
